    "description": "〝绯夜传奇〞变得更加易于游玩后再次问世！<br>向夺走一切的救世主复仇――<br>救世主的登场让王国逐渐恢复秩序，一名怀有血海深仇的女性在王国中驱驰。<br>在壮大的世界观中，主角薇尔贝特与她身边富有个性的角色交织出颇具深度的故事。<br>〝坚持自我原则而活的RPG〞再次启动――<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆一个关于〝感情与法理〞的故事</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331020/extras/589dc2dcd517400137ef9e939f8ddb80.poster.avif?t=1772147146\" width=780 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331020/extras/589dc2dcd517400137ef9e939f8ddb80.webm?t=1772147146\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331020/extras/589dc2dcd517400137ef9e939f8ddb80.mp4?t=1772147146\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>是要顺从感情横冲直撞，或是遵守依据法理的秩序？<br>以任何人皆有的感性与理性冲突为主题，描写心怀强烈感情勇往直前的薇尔贝特，与贯彻法理坚守世界秩序之人的对立。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆充满爽快感的战斗系统</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331020/extras/4710141ecdd362b5fd1ce3ccae9d3152.poster.avif?t=1772147146\" width=780 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331020/extras/4710141ecdd362b5fd1ce3ccae9d3152.webm?t=1772147146\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331020/extras/4710141ecdd362b5fd1ce3ccae9d3152.mp4?t=1772147146\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>本作的战斗系统，可配合自身游戏风格〝自由自在〞设置术技，施展形形色色的连击。<br>此外，透过夺取敌人名为〝心魂〞的图示，更可创造超越连击上限的组合技。任何人皆能轻松享受充满爽快感的战斗乐趣。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆维持原有感动的同时，变得更加易于游玩</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331020/extras/99f2fac56a7871d7f4da3217477f9c38.poster.avif?t=1772147146\" width=780 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331020/extras/99f2fac56a7871d7f4da3217477f9c38.webm?t=1772147146\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331020/extras/99f2fac56a7871d7f4da3217477f9c38.mp4?t=1772147146\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>增加各种方便的新功能，如显示目的地的图标，以及关闭原野或迷宫内遇敌的功能。<br>系列作必备的〝GRADE商店〞也于游戏初期便已开放，让玩家获得更顺畅的游玩体验。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆收录众多初版下载内容</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331020/extras/28872ab4732e1b16063bf82e4d70c528.poster.avif?t=1772147146\" width=780 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331020/extras/28872ab4732e1b16063bf82e4d70c528.webm?t=1772147146\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331020/extras/28872ab4732e1b16063bf82e4d70c528.mp4?t=1772147146\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>游戏本体收录众多初版下载内容。（※部分下载内容并未包含）<br>从能化身为系列作熟悉角色的服装到用处多多的道具，丰富内容帮助玩家进一步体验游戏乐趣。<br><br>※本商品是以2016年发售的〝绯夜传奇〞为基础开发的产品。（部分样式会稍有不同。）<br>※基本上为1人游玩，战斗时最多可4人游玩。",
